item.title: You Are not funny
item.description: Perhaps you have seen it happen online? Someone posts a comment and then appends the phrase ‘It’s a joke’ or ‘Humour for the humour impaired’ or some variant. I’m not talking about the people that post some deplorable remark and then try to dissemble their way clear of critique by claiming to be a humorist.
